{"tid":539778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察通例第6章31條 - 警務人員須時刻注意行為舉止和衣著儀表","createTime":"2018-01-25T00:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T01:26:01.000Z","uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54a5c9bd755580f6595c2ac8bb274c68deaf1d96","tid":539778,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo006.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo006.pdf&d=H94%2BgzYnyCrPm1IqZrKhgosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=40c6155e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo006.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n29. 除了實際執行槍械庫、羈留室守衞或醫院羈留病房的職務時，值勤的軍裝或 便衣警務人員獲准攜帶吸煙用物品。<br />\n<br />\n30. 軍裝部的初級警務人員穿著制服或便服當值時，除非獲得督察或以上職級人 員的批准，否則不得攜帶金錢超逾 1,000 元。於若干警署，如某更分非由督察或以上職級 人員管理，此項授權可由警署警長或主管警長作出。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>31. 除須喬裝打扮以執行職務外，警務人員須時刻注意行為舉止和衣著儀表，以 維護警隊的聲譽。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n32. 警務人員如在執行職務時接獲任何款項或財物，須迅速據實呈報。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n唔知休班警煽動人屌老母駛唔駛停職呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔駛，係唔係代表當眾屌人老母係可以維護警隊聲譽呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bd3ec9117cacef829d52ebd2dd47d2d0cc5163","tid":539778,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10b8d05d02fa373df1e1796042f6349c883c917e","tid":539778,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"警犬聲譽=0，唔存在嘅野係唔需要維護，所以當場屌人老母冇問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac02e2ba4dfa641a958a1ae3368702d8b1d6db33","tid":539778,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":